1
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:33,000
"Bittersweet Love"

2
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,400
(Episode 2)

3
00:02:04,231 --> 00:02:06,356
The stock market is just as hot today.

4
00:02:06,564 --> 00:02:08,106
The index jumped

5
00:02:08,272 --> 00:02:10,188
232.26 points today,

6
00:02:10,189 --> 00:02:11,730
finishing at

7
00:02:11,731 --> 00:02:14,230
9,743.51.

8
00:02:14,231 --> 00:02:15,231
Hey, Lüqing.

9
00:02:15,522 --> 00:02:16,762
You've spent time in Gangcheng.

10
00:02:17,224 --> 00:02:19,304
What do you think the
people there are really after?

11
00:02:19,397 --> 00:02:21,272
I'd say they're just testing the waters.

12
00:02:21,356 --> 00:02:22,707
Haven't heard the old man mention it.

13
00:02:22,731 --> 00:02:24,231
Gangcheng people are very sharp.

14
00:02:24,647 --> 00:02:26,897
Gangcheng's finance aligns with the globe.

15
00:02:27,397 --> 00:02:28,564
It even runs in parallel.

16
00:02:29,272 --> 00:02:29,856
They must have

17
00:02:29,857 --> 00:02:31,397
information we're not privy to.

18
00:02:31,564 --> 00:02:33,124
Bucked the trend right out of the gate.

19
00:02:33,231 --> 00:02:34,522
Pulled in a flood of hot money.

20
00:02:35,147 --> 00:02:35,939
Zhuo Xin,

21
00:02:36,106 --> 00:02:39,597
you'd better go home
and pump the old man for news.

22
00:02:39,765 --> 00:02:41,052
Uncle Zhuo can’t be in the dark.

23
00:02:41,397 --> 00:02:41,856
Bro,

24
00:02:42,106 --> 00:02:43,106
I've finished the...

25
00:02:44,272 --> 00:02:45,189
Oh wow!

26
00:02:45,231 --> 00:02:46,231
Lüqing.

27
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:48,022
Someone new in the family, huh?

28
00:02:48,314 --> 00:02:49,394
Never seen this one before.

29
00:02:53,814 --> 00:02:54,814
Xiaofan,

30
00:02:55,314 --> 00:02:56,314
come sit down.

31
00:03:12,397 --> 00:03:12,814
Hi there.

32
00:03:13,022 --> 00:03:14,063
I'm Lin Ziyang.

33
00:03:14,064 --> 00:03:14,731
Pleased to meet you.

34
00:03:14,814 --> 00:03:16,134
Looking forward to getting to it.

35
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:16,981
Hello.

36
00:03:17,189 --> 00:03:18,189
Hello.

37
00:03:19,981 --> 00:03:20,564
Lüqing.

38
00:03:20,814 --> 00:03:21,814
You guys

39
00:03:21,856 --> 00:03:22,856
are all so fun!

40
00:03:23,606 --> 00:03:24,439
Ziyang.

41
00:03:24,606 --> 00:03:25,926
You’re a real jack of all trades.

42
00:03:26,106 --> 00:03:27,522
You fit right in anywhere.

43
00:03:27,689 --> 00:03:28,147
Hey.

44
00:03:28,231 --> 00:03:29,481
Now that's unfair.

45
00:03:29,689 --> 00:03:31,189
I've got good taste.

46
00:03:31,481 --> 00:03:33,772
We’re talking about
Senior Brother Bei’s folks.

47
00:03:34,147 --> 00:03:35,271
Every one of them’s

48
00:03:35,272 --> 00:03:36,606
worth getting close to.

49
00:03:37,689 --> 00:03:38,689
Xiaofan.

50
00:03:39,356 --> 00:03:40,356
Got a question for you.

51
00:03:40,522 --> 00:03:41,522
So, what's your take

52
00:03:41,731 --> 00:03:42,731
on Gangcheng

53
00:03:42,856 --> 00:03:44,564
investing heavily

54
00:03:44,939 --> 00:03:45,939
in the mainland soon?

55
00:03:50,647 --> 00:03:51,647
I

56
00:03:52,356 --> 00:03:53,356
I-I

57
00:03:58,106 --> 00:03:59,731
I-I think

58
00:04:02,772 --> 00:04:03,981
our country

59
00:04:04,147 --> 00:04:07,272
is in a tough spot.

60
00:04:07,564 --> 00:04:11,147
Foreign funds may not help.

61
00:04:15,647 --> 00:04:16,814
Well then, Xiaofan...

62
00:04:16,939 --> 00:04:17,939
Xiaofan.

63
00:04:18,522 --> 00:04:20,002
Have you finished your practice test?

64
00:04:21,564 --> 00:04:22,564
Mm.

65
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,522
Leave your test here.

66
00:04:24,731 --> 00:04:25,856
Go study your English.

67
00:04:45,939 --> 00:04:46,606
To keep up with

68
00:04:46,607 --> 00:04:48,272
the minds of these princelings,

69
00:04:48,564 --> 00:04:50,355
Lu Xiaofan bought newspapers

70
00:04:50,356 --> 00:04:51,356
and read them thoroughly.

71
00:04:51,397 --> 00:04:53,397
Jotting down what he wanted to say.

72
00:04:53,772 --> 00:04:54,231
But

73
00:04:54,564 --> 00:04:56,189
the first word he memorized

74
00:04:56,481 --> 00:04:57,481
was "brother".

75
00:05:38,961 --> 00:05:40,294
Go buy some alcohol.

76
00:06:16,231 --> 00:06:17,911
What have you been up to out there lately?

77
00:06:19,731 --> 00:06:21,314
Aunt Lin had me take soup over.

78
00:06:21,481 --> 00:06:22,439
He's been busy lately.

79
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,439
Hardly gets to go home.

80
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,897
Lapdog.

81
00:06:30,022 --> 00:06:31,606
Real pro at sucking up, aren't you?

82
00:06:33,522 --> 00:06:34,314
Lüqing.

83
00:06:34,522 --> 00:06:35,856
Is Lu Xiaofan

84
00:06:36,314 --> 00:06:38,356
your brother-in-law or wife?

85
00:06:38,647 --> 00:06:40,188
Soup, porridge,

86
00:06:40,189 --> 00:06:41,356
and he does the washing too.

87
00:06:43,106 --> 00:06:44,356
He's a country boy.

88
00:06:44,397 --> 00:06:46,606
He can't find his spot in our family.

89
00:06:46,981 --> 00:06:47,897
If he wants to do it,

90
00:06:47,939 --> 00:06:48,939
he's free to go ahead.

91
00:06:51,147 --> 00:06:52,731
Listen up, Lüqing.

92
00:06:52,856 --> 00:06:53,939
If this keeps up,

93
00:06:54,064 --> 00:06:55,355
it'll ruin

94
00:06:55,356 --> 00:06:56,356
your reputation

95
00:06:56,357 --> 00:06:58,106
as the big man on campus.

96
00:06:58,606 --> 00:07:00,064
I can put up with the rest.

97
00:07:00,356 --> 00:07:02,188
Every time he speaks at the salon,

98
00:07:02,189 --> 00:07:04,481
I bite my tongue till I nearly bleed!

99
00:07:05,772 --> 00:07:06,772
I think

100
00:07:06,856 --> 00:07:08,438
our country

101
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:09,522
is in a tough spot.

102
00:07:09,897 --> 00:07:12,189
Politics gets brought up
at least ten times a night.

103
00:07:12,897 --> 00:07:13,772
I think so too.

104
00:07:13,772 --> 00:07:14,689
It’s really serious.

105
00:07:14,690 --> 00:07:15,897
It really is very serious.

106
00:07:17,147 --> 00:07:18,147
Alright, alright.

107
00:07:18,397 --> 00:07:19,189
Is it really necessary?

108
00:07:19,356 --> 00:07:20,147
So what?

109
00:07:20,356 --> 00:07:21,438
Are you saying

110
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:23,105
folks from the countryside

111
00:07:23,106 --> 00:07:25,146
aren't allowed to have an
opinion on world affairs?

112
00:07:27,064 --> 00:07:28,064
Still, Lüqing.

113
00:07:28,064 --> 00:07:28,772
About that.

114
00:07:28,773 --> 00:07:31,314
The trade director's son
from the development zone

115
00:07:31,481 --> 00:07:33,231
wants to join our salon too.

116
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,356
He went to Zhuo Xin on his own,

117
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,439
bringing gifts

118
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,731
and treating him to dinner.

119
00:07:37,772 --> 00:07:39,856
And Zhuo Xin turned him down flat.

120
00:07:40,064 --> 00:07:41,938
He was worried that type of person

121
00:07:41,939 --> 00:07:42,981
would drag our salon down.

122
00:07:43,856 --> 00:07:46,040
If your brother-in-law cracks
jokes at our salon again,

123
00:07:46,064 --> 00:07:47,064
word will get around.

124
00:07:47,189 --> 00:07:48,813
Here we are puffing ourselves up,

125
00:07:48,814 --> 00:07:50,647
acting like we're so refined.

126
00:07:50,772 --> 00:07:51,896
And it turns out

127
00:07:51,897 --> 00:07:52,522
people will think

128
00:07:52,523 --> 00:07:54,439
we're just a comedy club.

129
00:07:54,481 --> 00:07:56,689
Lu Xiaofan just brings shame on us.

130
00:07:56,897 --> 00:07:57,772
Just looking at him annoys me.

131
00:07:57,772 --> 00:07:58,356
Seriously.

132
00:07:58,357 --> 00:07:59,517
Is it really that big a deal?

133
00:08:00,106 --> 00:08:01,355
I'm just enjoying the novelty.

134
00:08:01,356 --> 00:08:02,606
It won't last long.

135
00:08:03,231 --> 00:08:04,355
You know he's not on our level,

136
00:08:04,356 --> 00:08:05,556
and yet you still pick on him.

137
00:08:06,272 --> 00:08:07,952
When a duck wanders into a flock of swans,

138
00:08:08,106 --> 00:08:10,272
nobody actually thinks you're ducks.

139
00:08:10,522 --> 00:08:12,562
Unless you were just big
white ducks to begin with.

140
00:08:13,064 --> 00:08:15,147
Fine, so long as you know.

141
00:08:22,189 --> 00:08:23,230
I'll leave you to it.

142
00:08:23,231 --> 00:08:23,522
Hey.

143
00:08:23,522 --> 00:08:24,522
Lüqing.

144
00:08:28,939 --> 00:08:30,231
I'm just enjoying the novelty.

145
00:08:30,272 --> 00:08:31,792
The novelty will wear off soon enough.

146
00:08:38,981 --> 00:08:39,981
As the saying goes,

147
00:08:40,272 --> 00:08:41,897
birds of a feather flock together.

148
00:08:42,897 --> 00:08:45,314
But Xiaofan still holds a glimmer of hope.

149
00:08:45,814 --> 00:08:47,397
Xiaofan knows they are worlds apart,

150
00:08:47,897 --> 00:08:50,856
like clouds and mud.

151
00:08:58,022 --> 00:08:59,147
Good work lately.

152
00:08:59,772 --> 00:09:00,856
Keep it up.

153
00:09:02,939 --> 00:09:03,939
Mm.

154
00:09:07,706 --> 00:09:10,799
[Recipies for Guangdong
slow-simmer soups]

155
00:09:13,772 --> 00:09:14,939
I don't like scallions.

156
00:09:19,356 --> 00:09:20,356
Bro,

157
00:09:20,814 --> 00:09:22,439
you-you drank the soup.

158
00:09:23,606 --> 00:09:25,106
Stay away from such books.

159
00:09:25,564 --> 00:09:27,147
Your studies are the most
important thing right now.

160
00:09:27,772 --> 00:09:28,772
Got it, bro.

161
00:09:33,856 --> 00:09:35,176
Join me at the salon from now on.

162
00:09:38,022 --> 00:09:39,022
Maybe not, bro.

163
00:09:39,647 --> 00:09:40,647
I

164
00:09:41,481 --> 00:09:42,897
I'm afraid I'll embarrass you.

165
00:09:46,939 --> 00:09:48,356
Just sit next to me.

166
00:09:48,814 --> 00:09:50,522
Listen more, speak less.

167
00:10:12,314 --> 00:10:13,647
Acting like a real student.

168
00:10:13,731 --> 00:10:15,051
Such a clueless look on his face.

169
00:10:22,897 --> 00:10:23,356
Right here.

170
00:10:23,606 --> 00:10:25,526
You need to use "that"
to form an object clause,

171
00:10:25,981 --> 00:10:28,147
and it's also the subject of the clause.

172
00:10:35,481 --> 00:10:36,481
What did I just say?

173
00:10:38,897 --> 00:10:39,897
You need

174
00:10:40,231 --> 00:10:41,022
to use

175
00:10:41,147 --> 00:10:42,147
a clause.

176
00:10:46,981 --> 00:10:47,981
And then?

177
00:10:50,106 --> 00:10:51,106
And then.

178
00:10:51,981 --> 00:10:52,981
And then.

179
00:10:53,856 --> 00:10:55,064
Let's stop here for today.

180
00:10:55,897 --> 00:10:56,897
Bro,

181
00:10:57,564 --> 00:10:58,814
wait here just a moment.

182
00:11:01,647 --> 00:11:02,647
Wait for me.

183
00:11:20,564 --> 00:11:21,981
Just in time.

184
00:11:23,606 --> 00:11:24,106
Bro,

185
00:11:24,356 --> 00:11:25,356
give it a try.

186
00:11:31,689 --> 00:11:32,814
These days,

187
00:11:33,231 --> 00:11:33,981
bro,

188
00:11:33,982 --> 00:11:35,606
thanks for tutoring me.

189
00:11:36,564 --> 00:11:37,856
Aunt Lin told me

190
00:11:38,481 --> 00:11:39,356
that you like

191
00:11:39,397 --> 00:11:40,439
stewed soup.

192
00:11:41,522 --> 00:11:42,522
So

193
00:11:42,647 --> 00:11:43,647
I just...

194
00:11:45,772 --> 00:11:47,897
I’ve been tutoring you,

195
00:11:53,147 --> 00:11:54,856
so outsiders won't know

196
00:11:56,772 --> 00:11:58,647
you have no schooling.

197
00:12:06,106 --> 00:12:07,106
Alright.

198
00:12:07,356 --> 00:12:08,356
Go get some rest.

199
00:13:02,647 --> 00:13:03,856
As we all know,

200
00:13:04,147 --> 00:13:06,230
Xiaofan's international perspective

201
00:13:06,231 --> 00:13:08,314
has always been remarkably insightful.

202
00:13:08,814 --> 00:13:09,564
Why not

203
00:13:09,814 --> 00:13:11,481
let Xiaofan

204
00:13:11,689 --> 00:13:12,689
start us off today?

205
00:13:12,731 --> 00:13:13,522
What do you say?

206
00:13:13,689 --> 00:13:14,522
Enough.

207
00:13:14,523 --> 00:13:15,564
Give it a rest.

208
00:13:16,647 --> 00:13:17,397
Aunt Lin.

209
00:13:17,606 --> 00:13:18,606
Pour us some water.

210
00:13:18,939 --> 00:13:19,939
I'll do it.

211
00:13:32,356 --> 00:13:33,356
Aunt Lin,

212
00:13:33,397 --> 00:13:35,147
get me a roast duck too.

213
00:13:35,231 --> 00:13:36,231
I'll go.

214
00:13:40,397 --> 00:13:40,939
Mom.

215
00:13:41,147 --> 00:13:42,731
I'm doing really well in Yunjing.

216
00:13:43,564 --> 00:13:44,772
Uncle Bei treats me very well.

217
00:13:45,064 --> 00:13:46,397
Brother Bei treats me well too.

218
00:13:47,314 --> 00:13:48,855
So don't worry about me.

219
00:13:48,856 --> 00:13:51,106
Go home early with Dad.

220
00:13:51,731 --> 00:13:52,731
Xiaofan.

221
00:13:52,939 --> 00:13:53,731
Could you

222
00:13:53,732 --> 00:13:55,612
ask uncle Bei to write a
recommendation letter?

223
00:13:56,272 --> 00:13:57,731
Pingping is about to graduate soon.

224
00:13:58,106 --> 00:14:00,314
Job assignments need
to be lined up in advance.

225
00:14:00,647 --> 00:14:02,689
Ask uncle Bei for advice.

226
00:14:03,856 --> 00:14:04,481
Mom.

227
00:14:04,814 --> 00:14:06,438
My schooling

228
00:14:06,439 --> 00:14:09,314
has troubled the Beis enough.

229
00:14:09,731 --> 00:14:10,981
We're useless.

230
00:14:11,397 --> 00:14:13,105
We can take care of one son

231
00:14:13,106 --> 00:14:14,397
but not the other.

232
00:14:14,856 --> 00:14:16,439
I hate to be a bother to you.

233
00:14:16,856 --> 00:14:18,689
Is this hard for you, Fanfan?

234
00:14:19,064 --> 00:14:20,564
No, no, not at all, Mom.

235
00:14:20,856 --> 00:14:22,022
Don't overthink it.

236
00:14:23,939 --> 00:14:24,939
I

237
00:14:26,106 --> 00:14:27,606
I'll go ask uncle Bei.

238
00:14:28,939 --> 00:14:30,521
I'll come by the shop in a few days

239
00:14:30,522 --> 00:14:31,522
and give you a call.

240
00:14:31,772 --> 00:14:33,356
Take care of yourself, Xiaofan.

241
00:14:35,481 --> 00:14:36,481
Okay.

242
00:14:39,314 --> 00:14:40,314
You've risen to the sky in one leap.

243
00:14:40,315 --> 00:14:42,272
How are you still acting
like such a bumpkin?

244
00:14:58,981 --> 00:15:00,181
The soup's about to boil over.

245
00:15:04,106 --> 00:15:04,564
Bro.

246
00:15:04,981 --> 00:15:06,647
The soup will be ready soon.

247
00:15:07,022 --> 00:15:08,481
I'll bring it over at dinnertime.

248
00:15:10,189 --> 00:15:11,189
About your brother,

249
00:15:11,731 --> 00:15:13,064
I'll talk to Dad.

250
00:15:15,106 --> 00:15:16,564
Bro, how did you know?

251
00:15:19,481 --> 00:15:21,772
The two floors share the same phone line.

252
00:15:23,022 --> 00:15:25,731
I've learned many new soup recipes.

253
00:15:26,647 --> 00:15:28,007
I can cook soup for you every day.

254
00:15:29,647 --> 00:15:31,127
I won't be home for dinner this week.

255
00:15:32,856 --> 00:15:34,147
The salon has moved to campus.

256
00:15:34,356 --> 00:15:35,796
I can't make it home in the evening.

257
00:15:36,689 --> 00:15:37,522
I see.

258
00:15:37,689 --> 00:15:39,022
If you're heading to campus,

259
00:15:39,606 --> 00:15:40,856
uncle Wu can give you a ride.

260
00:15:50,772 --> 00:15:52,564
Join me at the salon from now on.

261
00:15:55,397 --> 00:15:56,397
Bro.

262
00:15:59,147 --> 00:16:01,785
Is that little lackey of yours
becoming your personal assistant now?

263
00:16:02,231 --> 00:16:03,689
He's come all the way to school.

264
00:16:04,522 --> 00:16:06,064
He's only here to drop off my meal.

265
00:16:09,272 --> 00:16:09,731
Bro.

266
00:16:10,064 --> 00:16:10,522
Hey now.

267
00:16:10,647 --> 00:16:11,272
Xiaofan.

268
00:16:11,439 --> 00:16:12,606
Don't rush.

269
00:16:12,981 --> 00:16:15,481
A few more minutes won't make him hungry.

270
00:16:16,356 --> 00:16:16,981
Bro,

271
00:16:16,982 --> 00:16:18,147
where are you eating?

272
00:16:18,439 --> 00:16:19,522
The dorm or the cafeteria?

273
00:16:19,606 --> 00:16:20,439
After you finish eating,

274
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,731
I'll take the container back,

275
00:16:21,897 --> 00:16:23,106
no need to trouble yourself.

276
00:16:25,606 --> 00:16:27,064
I'll take it back tonight.

277
00:16:28,022 --> 00:16:29,314
Why go to so much trouble?

278
00:16:29,439 --> 00:16:31,022
He brought the soup all the way here.

279
00:16:31,064 --> 00:16:33,189
Come eat with us in the cafeteria.

280
00:16:34,689 --> 00:16:35,689
Bro,

281
00:16:35,981 --> 00:16:37,314
I'll head back then.

282
00:16:37,731 --> 00:16:38,731
Hold on.

283
00:16:39,022 --> 00:16:40,022
Oh.

284
00:16:42,231 --> 00:16:43,731
Call Mrs. Lu when you're home.

285
00:16:44,772 --> 00:16:46,892
I've written an introduction
letter for your brother.

286
00:16:47,022 --> 00:16:47,814
Once he graduates,

287
00:16:47,815 --> 00:16:49,335
he can take his diploma and the letter

288
00:16:49,731 --> 00:16:51,331
to report to the county textile factory.

289
00:16:52,022 --> 00:16:53,022
Thank you, bro.

290
00:16:53,231 --> 00:16:54,481
I'll go call her right now.

291
00:17:00,689 --> 00:17:01,564
His looks

292
00:17:01,565 --> 00:17:03,522
are nothing special.

293
00:17:09,314 --> 00:17:10,314
Tastes pretty good.

294
00:17:11,272 --> 00:17:12,272
Bei...!

295
00:17:13,106 --> 00:17:14,522
It hasn't even been that long.

296
00:17:15,272 --> 00:17:16,439
I mean the soup.

297
00:17:18,272 --> 00:17:19,272
Xiaofan.

298
00:17:19,772 --> 00:17:20,772
Xiaofan.

299
00:17:21,189 --> 00:17:22,771
Lüxin called to ask you pick her up.

300
00:17:22,772 --> 00:17:24,438
I wrote down the address for you.

301
00:17:24,439 --> 00:17:25,439
Take a taxi.

302
00:17:26,814 --> 00:17:27,856
Oh, Xiaofan.

303
00:17:28,022 --> 00:17:29,105
I could tell from her voice

304
00:17:29,106 --> 00:17:30,438
she'd had one too many.

305
00:17:30,439 --> 00:17:31,439
Be careful.

306
00:17:31,689 --> 00:17:32,689
Alright.

307
00:17:58,814 --> 00:17:59,814
Lüxin.

308
00:18:07,314 --> 00:18:08,897
Who's this?

309
00:18:12,772 --> 00:18:13,772
Lüxin.

310
00:18:18,439 --> 00:18:19,606
This guy

311
00:18:20,522 --> 00:18:22,897
is my husband.

312
00:18:25,814 --> 00:18:26,939
My dear father

313
00:18:27,106 --> 00:18:30,231
found me such a wonderful husband.

314
00:18:34,439 --> 00:18:35,439
Lüxin.

315
00:18:35,647 --> 00:18:36,689
It's getting late.

316
00:18:36,981 --> 00:18:38,564
Let me take you home.

317
00:18:39,981 --> 00:18:41,731
Go away.

318
00:18:43,064 --> 00:18:44,606
How dare you!

319
00:18:50,606 --> 00:18:53,314
Yeah, some husband you are.

320
00:19:00,856 --> 00:19:01,856
What a joke.

321
00:19:06,022 --> 00:19:06,981
Just leave.

322
00:19:06,982 --> 00:19:08,731
Don't push your luck.

323
00:19:09,397 --> 00:19:11,064
Stay away from Bei Lüqing.

324
00:19:13,064 --> 00:19:14,356
My brother's just

325
00:19:16,772 --> 00:19:18,772
being polite to you, nothing else.

326
00:19:20,314 --> 00:19:21,730
Don't push your luck.

327
00:19:21,731 --> 00:19:22,855
Don't mess with his life.

328
00:19:22,856 --> 00:19:23,856
Got it?

329
00:19:24,689 --> 00:19:25,731
Don't push your luck.

330
00:19:26,272 --> 00:19:27,314
You got that?

331
00:19:27,731 --> 00:19:29,064
Now get lost.

332
00:19:29,147 --> 00:19:30,772
Yeah, what are you even doing here?

333
00:19:30,814 --> 00:19:32,231
What are you hanging around for?

334
00:19:33,356 --> 00:19:34,772
Just go already.

335
00:20:01,564 --> 00:20:02,814
I'm sorry, bro.

336
00:20:06,356 --> 00:20:07,564
I don't have any money on me.

337
00:20:09,189 --> 00:20:10,439
They need to pay the bill.

338
00:20:11,481 --> 00:20:13,064
I only remembered your number.

339
00:20:20,147 --> 00:20:21,439
Wipe first.

340
00:20:31,314 --> 00:20:32,314
What happened?

341
00:20:36,439 --> 00:20:37,439
It's all my fault.

342
00:20:39,314 --> 00:20:40,314
I'm sorry.

343
00:20:42,022 --> 00:20:43,856
I made Lüxin angry.

344
00:20:45,939 --> 00:20:46,939
Where's Bei Lüxin?

345
00:20:55,856 --> 00:20:56,856
Lüqing.

346
00:20:56,897 --> 00:20:57,981
I just got a call.

347
00:20:58,147 --> 00:20:59,147
Where are you?

348
00:20:59,314 --> 00:21:00,481
Lüxin has had a miscarriage.

349
00:21:01,397 --> 00:21:02,814
Don't tell Xiaofan yet.

350
00:21:02,939 --> 00:21:04,147
Get over here quickly.

351
00:21:05,981 --> 00:21:07,064
Lüxin had a fall.

352
00:21:07,564 --> 00:21:08,564
She's at the hospital.

353
00:21:09,231 --> 00:21:10,231
You go back first.

354
00:21:10,564 --> 00:21:11,604
I need to head over there.

355
00:21:12,106 --> 00:21:13,272
Is the baby okay?

356
00:21:18,022 --> 00:21:19,272
I'm sorry, bro.

357
00:21:32,439 --> 00:21:33,856
You know, you Lu family folks

358
00:21:36,189 --> 00:21:37,309
aren't as dumb as I thought.

359
00:21:38,897 --> 00:21:39,897
Being useful

360
00:21:40,022 --> 00:21:41,731
was Lu Xiaofan's only reassurance

361
00:21:41,814 --> 00:21:44,522
to stay in the Bei household.

362
00:21:45,939 --> 00:21:47,564
Now Lu Xiaofan realized

363
00:21:47,939 --> 00:21:49,313
he had no grounds or reason

364
00:21:49,314 --> 00:21:50,772
to stay in the Bei family.

365
00:21:51,897 --> 00:21:53,814
But once Lu Xiaofan made up his mind,

366
00:21:54,356 --> 00:21:56,189
a hint of reluctance welled up inside him.

367
00:21:57,731 --> 00:21:58,856
Reluctant about what?

368
00:21:58,981 --> 00:22:00,356
He couldn't quite figure it out.

369
00:22:01,731 --> 00:22:04,856
But leaving seemed inevitable.

370
00:22:09,731 --> 00:22:10,731
Bro.

371
00:22:11,022 --> 00:22:12,022
Are you leaving?

372
00:22:14,397 --> 00:22:15,397
I

373
00:22:16,522 --> 00:22:18,106
I'm useless now, aren't I?

374
00:22:19,522 --> 00:22:21,522
What use did you ever think you had?

375
00:22:29,106 --> 00:22:30,106
Bro,

376
00:22:31,022 --> 00:22:34,022
about my brother's job.

377
00:22:36,564 --> 00:22:37,814
Mom wanted to

378
00:22:38,314 --> 00:22:39,814
ask about it today.

379
00:22:40,356 --> 00:22:41,855
She's asking if our promise

380
00:22:41,856 --> 00:22:43,189
will still be kept.

381
00:22:43,481 --> 00:22:44,814
Will the Bei family

382
00:22:45,064 --> 00:22:46,606
still honor this marriage?

383
00:22:46,731 --> 00:22:47,731
No.

384
00:22:48,564 --> 00:22:50,021
We've already brought

385
00:22:50,022 --> 00:22:51,397
plenty of trouble to uncle Bei.

386
00:22:52,064 --> 00:22:53,064
As for my mom,

387
00:22:54,064 --> 00:22:55,481
I'll explain things clearly to her.

388
00:22:55,814 --> 00:22:57,189
Your mom won't agree to let you leave.

389
00:22:59,981 --> 00:23:00,981
Yeah.

390
00:23:04,564 --> 00:23:06,022
Your worth

391
00:23:06,939 --> 00:23:08,481
is decided by yourself.

392
00:23:10,147 --> 00:23:11,314
Where your value lies

393
00:23:11,772 --> 00:23:13,012
is for you to find on your own.

394
00:23:15,106 --> 00:23:16,146
Father is waiting for you.

395
00:23:27,231 --> 00:23:28,022
Xiaofan,

396
00:23:28,023 --> 00:23:29,564
come, sit down and let's talk.

397
00:23:36,772 --> 00:23:38,063
Since it's come to this,

398
00:23:38,064 --> 00:23:39,564
let's be frank.

399
00:23:41,481 --> 00:23:43,897
You know why the Bei family took you in.

400
00:23:45,522 --> 00:23:46,772
You understand

401
00:23:47,897 --> 00:23:48,897
the situation now.

402
00:23:54,481 --> 00:23:56,564
We always keep our promises.

403
00:23:57,314 --> 00:23:58,814
You can stay and finish school.

404
00:23:59,522 --> 00:24:01,314
I'll get you a good job.

405
00:24:02,439 --> 00:24:03,439
Or

406
00:24:03,981 --> 00:24:05,147
take this money

407
00:24:05,897 --> 00:24:06,897
and head home.

408
00:24:11,981 --> 00:24:12,981
It's alright.

409
00:24:13,231 --> 00:24:15,189
Just say what's on your mind.

410
00:24:17,106 --> 00:24:18,271
There's no telling what trouble Lüxin

411
00:24:18,272 --> 00:24:19,522
might cause later on.

412
00:24:20,231 --> 00:24:21,522
Having him just in name

413
00:24:22,397 --> 00:24:23,397
has its uses.

414
00:24:34,689 --> 00:24:36,089
I want to stay with the Bei family.

415
00:24:39,814 --> 00:24:41,106
Then everything stays as it is.

416
00:24:41,731 --> 00:24:43,147
Focus on your exams.

417
00:25:05,189 --> 00:25:06,189
Aunt Lin,

418
00:25:06,272 --> 00:25:07,855
the bed feels a little hard.

419
00:25:07,856 --> 00:25:09,439
Please add one more cushion.

420
00:25:11,897 --> 00:25:12,897
Lüxin.

421
00:25:15,731 --> 00:25:16,731
Get out.

422
00:25:25,064 --> 00:25:26,064
Aunt Lin said

423
00:25:26,147 --> 00:25:27,271
you haven't been eating well lately.

424
00:25:27,272 --> 00:25:28,689
I told you to get out.

425
00:25:31,272 --> 00:25:32,439
I made some soup.

426
00:25:35,689 --> 00:25:36,939
Are you deaf or what?

427
00:25:54,231 --> 00:25:55,314
When are you heading back?

428
00:25:58,897 --> 00:25:59,981
Bro says

429
00:26:00,106 --> 00:26:01,689
wait till I finish my exams.

430
00:26:06,772 --> 00:26:08,021
You never cease to amaze me.

431
00:26:08,022 --> 00:26:09,022
Lu Xiaofan.

432
00:26:10,772 --> 00:26:12,397
Why do you keep bothering my brother?

433
00:26:13,522 --> 00:26:14,813
How dare you stay here

434
00:26:14,814 --> 00:26:15,897
and have another mouthful!

435
00:26:20,606 --> 00:26:21,606
Lüxin,

436
00:26:21,647 --> 00:26:23,981
let me take you back to your room.

437
00:26:44,814 --> 00:26:45,606
Lüxin,

438
00:26:45,607 --> 00:26:46,887
be careful, don't catch a chill.

439
00:26:54,522 --> 00:26:55,522
Bro and dad

440
00:26:55,856 --> 00:26:56,772
asked me to look after you.

441
00:26:56,773 --> 00:26:58,230
The child is gone now.

442
00:26:58,231 --> 00:26:59,689
I don't need a fake husband.

443
00:27:01,647 --> 00:27:02,647
Uncle Bei said

444
00:27:04,189 --> 00:27:05,439
no divorce for now.

445
00:27:06,022 --> 00:27:07,521
No divorce and keep it quiet.

446
00:27:07,522 --> 00:27:08,897
Do I need you to tell me that?

447
00:27:11,897 --> 00:27:13,689
I'm stuck in this dump

448
00:27:14,439 --> 00:27:15,231
just pretending

449
00:27:15,232 --> 00:27:16,481
I'm traveling overseas.

450
00:27:17,064 --> 00:27:18,856
Uncle Bei means well for you.

451
00:27:19,564 --> 00:27:20,564
Means well?

452
00:27:25,958 --> 00:27:26,958
Do you know why my mother

453
00:27:26,982 --> 00:27:29,022
only took my brother
to Gangcheng back then?

454
00:27:30,606 --> 00:27:31,272
I just wanted...

455
00:27:31,273 --> 00:27:33,272
I'm not Bei Mosha's biological daughter.

456
00:27:43,106 --> 00:27:44,022
To my mother

457
00:27:44,023 --> 00:27:45,063
and the Bei family,

458
00:27:45,064 --> 00:27:46,231
I'm nothing but a disgrace.

459
00:27:48,064 --> 00:27:49,772
Just like my lost baby.

460
00:27:52,897 --> 00:27:54,772
They don't care if I live or die.

461
00:27:55,022 --> 00:27:56,262
They don't mean well toward me.

462
00:27:57,314 --> 00:27:58,522
Now do you get it?

463
00:27:59,731 --> 00:28:01,439
Even as my husband,

464
00:28:01,897 --> 00:28:03,481
you stand to gain nothing.

465
00:28:04,022 --> 00:28:05,182
Get lost while you still can.

466
00:28:07,439 --> 00:28:08,647
No-no.

467
00:28:09,564 --> 00:28:11,189
Can't you have a shred of self-respect?

468
00:28:11,981 --> 00:28:14,189
You just want to profit from this title.

469
00:28:15,772 --> 00:28:17,106
I'm not after anything.

470
00:28:18,856 --> 00:28:20,814
I just want to be useful.

471
00:28:22,272 --> 00:28:23,606
Now I am useful.

472
00:28:24,397 --> 00:28:25,647
Useful to the Bei family,

473
00:28:26,897 --> 00:28:28,022
to you,

474
00:28:28,897 --> 00:28:30,189
and to bro too.

475
00:28:32,689 --> 00:28:33,855
As long as I can be of some use,

476
00:28:33,856 --> 00:28:34,981
I'll be content.

477
00:28:37,522 --> 00:28:38,814
I'm also very grateful to bro.

478
00:28:40,272 --> 00:28:41,272
For quite a while now,

479
00:28:41,689 --> 00:28:43,272
he's helped me a lot.

480
00:29:23,897 --> 00:29:25,564
Get some rest first.

481
00:29:26,939 --> 00:29:28,356
If the seasoning is right,

482
00:29:29,564 --> 00:29:30,314
I'll also...

483
00:29:30,315 --> 00:29:31,522
Do whatever you want.

484
00:29:32,397 --> 00:29:34,517
Just don't go thinking
you're part of the Bei family.

485
00:30:11,856 --> 00:30:12,856
Bro.

486
00:30:15,564 --> 00:30:16,564
Bro.

487
00:30:16,897 --> 00:30:17,897
I'm sorry.

488
00:30:18,272 --> 00:30:19,939
I've caused you trouble again.

489
00:30:32,189 --> 00:30:33,522
How's your exam prep going?

490
00:30:34,731 --> 00:30:35,731
Alright.

491
00:30:37,022 --> 00:30:38,064
Lüxin, she...

492
00:30:38,522 --> 00:30:40,106
You have the Gaokao in two months.

493
00:30:40,356 --> 00:30:41,814
Don't bring me soup anymore.

494
00:30:43,606 --> 00:30:44,606
No.

495
00:30:44,647 --> 00:30:45,647
It won't be a problem.

496
00:30:46,189 --> 00:30:48,481
I'll study first, then bring you soup.

497
00:30:49,064 --> 00:30:50,439
It won't affect my review.

498
00:30:54,481 --> 00:30:55,481
Whatever.

499
00:31:19,147 --> 00:31:20,397
This soup is fantastic.

500
00:31:20,522 --> 00:31:21,314
Xiaofan.

501
00:31:21,356 --> 00:31:22,688
You make it even better than I do.

502
00:31:22,689 --> 00:31:23,897
Did your mother teach you?

503
00:31:24,564 --> 00:31:26,189
The books spell everything out clearly.

504
00:31:26,397 --> 00:31:28,314
Whether it's too bland or too salty

505
00:31:28,397 --> 00:31:30,117
my brother will tell me after he tastes it.

506
00:31:31,731 --> 00:31:32,522
Bro,

507
00:31:32,689 --> 00:31:33,689
you're back.

508
00:31:39,522 --> 00:31:40,882
Your admission letter has arrived.

509
00:31:48,691 --> 00:31:51,931
[Yunjing People's University
Acceptance Letter]

510
00:31:55,606 --> 00:31:56,731
You really got in.

511
00:31:58,678 --> 00:32:00,265
[He got into Vocational Trade and Economics]

512
00:32:00,439 --> 00:32:02,519
Just fell a little short of
getting into an undergrad.

513
00:32:04,064 --> 00:32:05,064
It's okay.

514
00:32:05,439 --> 00:32:07,189
As long as I'm in the same school as you.

515
00:32:16,106 --> 00:32:16,647
Bro,

516
00:32:17,064 --> 00:32:18,064
try some.

517
00:32:33,439 --> 00:32:34,439
Come on!

518
00:32:36,064 --> 00:32:37,064
Come on!

519
00:32:37,939 --> 00:32:39,064
Come on! Bro.

520
00:33:23,814 --> 00:33:24,814
Wipe your sweat.

521
00:33:26,897 --> 00:33:27,897
Have some water.

522
00:33:32,106 --> 00:33:33,272
Why’s your voice hoarse?

523
00:33:33,689 --> 00:33:35,271
I cheered too hard for you.

524
00:33:35,272 --> 00:33:36,106
Lu Xiaofan.

525
00:33:36,189 --> 00:33:37,606
You're so biased.

526
00:33:37,897 --> 00:33:38,897
Where's mine?

527
00:33:40,272 --> 00:33:42,064
Does Young Master Lin need water?

528
00:33:42,272 --> 00:33:43,397
Fine, fine, fine.

529
00:33:43,481 --> 00:33:44,314
Who's that?

530
00:33:44,314 --> 00:33:45,231
He's from the countryside.

531
00:33:45,232 --> 00:33:46,647
And he's hanging around Mr. Bei.

532
00:33:46,981 --> 00:33:48,147
He's being way too eager.

533
00:33:48,397 --> 00:33:49,981
He's happy being a lackey.

534
00:33:50,981 --> 00:33:51,856
Don't talk nonsense.

535
00:33:51,897 --> 00:33:53,189
What do you mean, lackey?

536
00:33:53,314 --> 00:33:54,897
That's called logistics support.

537
00:33:57,064 --> 00:33:58,314
Logistics support, huh?

538
00:34:04,522 --> 00:34:05,689
Look, there he goes again.

539
00:34:06,731 --> 00:34:08,147
He's taking food to Mr. Bei.

540
00:34:08,814 --> 00:34:09,814
You even need to ask?

541
00:34:09,999 --> 00:34:12,083
I just saw him over there

542
00:34:12,107 --> 00:34:13,272
carrying meals for others.

543
00:34:13,397 --> 00:34:14,397
How embarrassing.

544
00:34:14,564 --> 00:34:16,564
He's disgraced our whole
vocational department.

545
00:34:17,064 --> 00:34:18,981
He likes being a yes-man.

546
00:34:20,439 --> 00:34:20,939
Bro,

547
00:34:21,022 --> 00:34:22,022
have this.

548
00:34:22,314 --> 00:34:23,355
This fish has fewer bones.

549
00:34:23,356 --> 00:34:24,396
Do you have enough to eat?

550
00:34:24,814 --> 00:34:25,814
Yeah.

551
00:34:28,689 --> 00:34:29,522
Eating this well, huh?

552
00:34:29,647 --> 00:34:30,939
Didn't bother to bring me any.

553
00:34:31,897 --> 00:34:32,689
I'll bring you some next time.

554
00:34:32,856 --> 00:34:33,856
It's a deal.

555
00:34:36,397 --> 00:34:37,397
Take a look at that.

556
00:34:37,481 --> 00:34:39,397
Over there he's eating like a king.

557
00:34:40,522 --> 00:34:42,188
Why even return to our dorm?

558
00:34:42,189 --> 00:34:43,231
Look at him.

559
00:34:43,356 --> 00:34:44,772
Serving tea and water.

560
00:34:45,064 --> 00:34:46,606
A regular little waiter.

561
00:34:46,731 --> 00:34:49,356
Serving as Mr. Bei's personal servant now.

562
00:34:49,606 --> 00:34:51,314
All to curry favor and join their family.

563
00:34:57,397 --> 00:34:58,397
Just eat.

564
00:35:15,522 --> 00:35:16,939
Has anyone seen my book?

565
00:35:17,064 --> 00:35:18,184
The one with the blue cover.

566
00:35:18,356 --> 00:35:19,356
And a water bottle too.

567
00:35:20,647 --> 00:35:21,772
Don't you think the cleaner

568
00:35:21,814 --> 00:35:23,146
threw them out as trash?

569
00:35:23,147 --> 00:35:24,147
Huh?

570
00:35:24,981 --> 00:35:26,771
The cleaner was here just now.

571
00:35:26,772 --> 00:35:27,564
Why not

572
00:35:27,565 --> 00:35:29,272
check the trash cans in the hallway?

573
00:35:29,647 --> 00:35:31,527
It'd be such a waste to
throw them away, right?

574
00:35:31,981 --> 00:35:32,439
Oh.

575
00:35:32,981 --> 00:35:33,981
I'll go take a look then.

576
00:35:38,439 --> 00:35:39,439
Ma'am.

577
00:35:51,939 --> 00:35:53,564
Now that's real environmentalism.

578
00:35:53,606 --> 00:35:55,314
Man and books, straight to the bin.

579
00:35:55,397 --> 00:35:56,147
Remember this.

580
00:35:56,148 --> 00:35:58,356
Stop embarrassing our department out there.

581
00:36:25,522 --> 00:36:26,522
Xiaofan.

582
00:36:27,314 --> 00:36:29,271
We're just talking about Iran right now.

583
00:36:29,272 --> 00:36:30,272
Come listen in.

584
00:36:31,522 --> 00:36:32,522
Mr. Ziyang.

585
00:36:33,064 --> 00:36:35,272
I really can't follow
what you're talking about.

586
00:36:35,897 --> 00:36:37,564
I'm just here to bring my bro books.

587
00:36:42,814 --> 00:36:44,147
The Iran question and all that.

588
00:36:44,272 --> 00:36:45,689
You'd better ask my bro.

589
00:36:46,314 --> 00:36:47,314
I'll be going now.

590
00:36:48,564 --> 00:36:49,896
How does a person

591
00:36:49,897 --> 00:36:51,647
like Lu Xiaofan even exist?

592
00:36:52,106 --> 00:36:53,106
Not even the Transformers

593
00:36:53,107 --> 00:36:54,397
change this completely.

594
00:36:55,189 --> 00:36:56,522
Aren't you pathetic?

595
00:36:56,814 --> 00:36:58,054
When he's around, you complain.

596
00:36:58,231 --> 00:36:59,606
When he's gone, you miss him.

597
00:37:00,522 --> 00:37:01,939
See that lawn back there?

598
00:37:02,939 --> 00:37:03,689
What about it?

599
00:37:03,690 --> 00:37:04,731
Go cool off over there.

600
00:37:05,981 --> 00:37:07,147
Hey, Lord Bei.

601
00:37:08,106 --> 00:37:09,355
Since when did you

602
00:37:09,356 --> 00:37:11,481
start sticking up for a nobody like that?

603
00:37:11,772 --> 00:37:13,896
Didn't you always loathe people

604
00:37:13,897 --> 00:37:15,063
who curry favor for gains,

605
00:37:15,064 --> 00:37:16,813
who just reach out for handouts

606
00:37:16,814 --> 00:37:17,564
live in humiliation

607
00:37:17,565 --> 00:37:18,981
and die in shame?

608
00:37:19,647 --> 00:37:20,439
Well.

609
00:37:20,647 --> 00:37:22,064
I'm still enjoying the novelty.

610
00:37:22,856 --> 00:37:23,647
Fine.

611
00:37:23,772 --> 00:37:24,772
Got it.

612
00:37:25,314 --> 00:37:26,314
Whenever Lord Bei

613
00:37:26,314 --> 00:37:27,064
gets tired of the novelty,

614
00:37:27,064 --> 00:37:28,064
just give us a heads up

615
00:37:28,106 --> 00:37:29,689
and we can stop gritting our teeth.

616
00:37:30,022 --> 00:37:31,064
Hey, wait.

617
00:37:31,731 --> 00:37:32,856
You really don't know?

618
00:37:33,897 --> 00:37:34,897
What?

619
00:37:35,231 --> 00:37:36,606
A while back,

620
00:37:37,022 --> 00:37:39,102
those punks from the tech
school beat Lu Xiaofan up.

621
00:37:39,147 --> 00:37:40,481
It's been a while now, hasn't it?

622
00:38:17,939 --> 00:38:19,397
Dear Teacher,

623
00:38:20,106 --> 00:38:22,106
I'm Lu Xiaofan, from the
vocational department.

624
00:38:23,022 --> 00:38:24,542
Due to special personal circumstances,

625
00:38:24,814 --> 00:38:27,231
I would like to request some time off.

626
00:38:28,439 --> 00:38:29,564
During my absence,

627
00:38:29,689 --> 00:38:32,106
I will make up all missed
classes and assignments.

628
00:38:33,064 --> 00:38:34,522
Please grant me this leave.

629
00:38:40,272 --> 00:38:41,272
Where are you going?

630
00:38:42,814 --> 00:38:43,397
I

631
00:38:43,647 --> 00:38:45,022
I'm on leave.

632
00:38:46,022 --> 00:38:47,022
Going home?

633
00:38:48,397 --> 00:38:49,397
No.

634
00:38:49,897 --> 00:38:50,731
I'm just going out...

635
00:38:50,732 --> 00:38:52,147
You gonna lay low for a while?

636
00:38:53,647 --> 00:38:54,647
Yeah.

637
00:38:55,231 --> 00:38:55,731
Come on.

638
00:38:55,732 --> 00:38:57,314
I'm taking you to watch the fun!

639
00:38:57,606 --> 00:38:58,606
Let's go.
